I've been unable to find the definition of `isIdenticalToWhenDefined` for `CallBase` or `CallInst`. I've checked `Instruction.cpp`, `Instructions.cpp`, `Instructions.h`, and `InstrTypes.h`. This is highly unusual.

Let's go back to the beginning. The crash is in `EarlyCSE.cpp`. The comparison logic is in `DenseMapInfo<SimpleValue>::isEqual`, which calls `isEqualImpl`, which calls `LHSI->isIdenticalToWhenDefined(RHSI, /*IntersectAttrs=*/true)`.

The problem is that `isIdenticalToWhenDefined` is returning true for two `call`s that differ only by the `strictfp` attribute when the intrinsic is commutative.

If the override doesn't exist, then the base `Instruction::isIdenticalToWhenDefined` is being called. Let's look at that again.
```cpp
bool Instruction::isIdenticalToWhenDefined(const Instruction *I,
                                           bool IntersectAttrs) const {
  if (getOpcode() != I->getOpcode() ||
      getNumOperands() != I->getNumOperands() || getType() != I->getType())
    return false;

  // If both instructions have no operands, they are identical.
  if (getNumOperands() == 0 && I->getNumOperands() == 0)
    return this->hasSameSpecialState(I, /*IgnoreAlignment=*/false,
                                     IntersectAttrs);

  // We have two instructions of identical opcode and #operands.  Check to see
  // if all operands are the same.
  if (!std::equal(op_begin(), op_end(), I->op_begin()))
    return false; // This is where it would fail for non-commutative calls.

  // ... PHI node logic ...

  return this->hasSameSpecialState(I, /*IgnoreAlignment=*/false,
                                   IntersectAttrs);
}
```
This base implementation does *not* handle commutativity. If the operands are swapped (`@llvm.smin(%a, %b)` vs `@llvm.smin(%b, %a)`), the `std::equal` check will fail. This means `isIdenticalToWhenDefined` must be returning `false`, and some *other* logic in `isEqualImpl` is handling the commutative case.

Let's re-examine `isEqualImpl` from `EarlyCSE.cpp`.
```bash
sed -n '/static bool isEqualImpl/,/}/p' llvm/lib/Transforms/Scalar/EarlyCSE.cpp
```

